

实现思路
* 从零开始zig+pipewire+decoder: 太有挑战性，太杀时间
* 借助mpv: ipc远程控制
* 借助zig+libmpv: 省掉ipc开销
* 借助mpd、cmus等cs架构的程序

必须要与nvim集成？
* tui 不也挺好吗

planned features
* playlist
    * edit playlist in a buffer
    * pattern for each line: "{name} :: {path}"
    * load track from a directory (recursively?)
        * supported format: mp3, m4a, flav, ape
    * saved as a file
* repeat/shuffle/switch/sort a playlist
* repeat/forward/backward/rewind a track
* pause/resume, mute/unmute, volume up/down
* tui or headless

rejected features
* metadata extracting: title, musican, album, duration, format, bit ...
* manipulating the underlying files
